\item $median = \frac{24 + 24}{2} = 24 $

\end{itemize}

The {\emph{median}} is the center score of the distribution.  Half of the values are below the median, and half are above the median in the distribution. 

What are the strengths and weaknesses of the median?

\begin{itemize}
\item Strength:  It is not sensitive to extreme values (\emph{outliers}).

