\subsubsection{Symmetric}

The dataset that has the attribute of symmetry has the following features: 

\begin{itemize}
\item Balanced Distribution
\item Often bell-shaped
\item The statistics (mean, median, and mode) have approximately the same value.
\end{itemize}

